Notes: 

1.How to run the script

It is necessary to run the scripts with the following command. 

$ python client_classes_150.py 


2.Dataset Download 

Please download the dataset on Kaggle with an registered account and save it into a designated directory. 


https://www.kaggle.com/thedagger/pokemon-generation-one

3.Dataset Quality

It is a sample dataset of pokemon with a quite larger dataset. However, some of the images has the warning as follows: 

PNG warning: iCCP: known incorrect sRGB profile

User can ignore the warning message. Otherwise, the users need to use ImageMagick to remove the bad images and then run the script. ImageMagick is an good tool but has a quite longer learning curve. 

